title: Clean spacious one bedroom in residential area
neighborhood: Spring Lake Park, Blaine, Mounds View
app_fee: $40 fee to include criminal, credit, eviction and employment check
posting_body: ['Top floor 1 bedroom in quiet 17-unit building.', 'Located in a residential area within walking distance to a theater and dining establishments.', 'Partially covered balcony.', 'Flooring includes a unique contrast of wood, tile, vinyl, and carpet.', 'Large apartment with bedroom large enough for a king-sized bed.', 'Many long term residents.', 'Soft water.', 'Pictures may be of similar apartments', 'Borders the cities of Blaine, Mounds View, and Fridley.', 'Call or text for private showing.', 'Cat or small dog considered with additional fees.', 'Qualifications generally include: 1) income of roughly 3 times the rent, 2) no felonies, 3) 600 credit score with no outstanding rental judgments and no evictions within 3 years, 4) clean housekeeping habits, 5) absolutely no smoking in the apartment, 6) maximum 2 occupants per bedroom, 7) pets under 20 pounds considered with additional monthly rent and damage deposit.', ' Management has the right to accept applicants which do not totally comply with the qualifications with additional security deposit and/or other changes to the lease conditions.']
